  m_Name: Chilli Conversation 2
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  SpeakerName: Yukio
  paragraphs:
  - "DAYUM I FEEL INCREDIBLE\u201D \u201Cyou are the most insane chef"
  - only the best for my best friend
  - PHEWWWWWWW i feel so good i am on fire
  - okay isagi, tell me about your night. did you do what i asked?
  - "oooh yes okay i\u2019ve been looking forward to this\u201D  \u201Cbut yes of
    course i did because i\u2019m the bestest in the whole world at what i do\u201D
    \u201Ci got in contact with Kenji - the detective you remember?"
  - of course
  - "right, well this guy was really strange but he agreed without hesitation\u201D
    \u201Cat this point so many detectives have turned us down this guy could be
    anyone and i\u2019d hire him"
  - "thank god, and i agree, i\u2019ve waited too long already. i miss him."
  - "its okay yukio, i\u2019m always here"
  - "\u2026"
  - except for right now, i got things (and the girl from last night) to do
  - right, have fun with that
  - "bye! and next time I WANT THE SAME THING\u201D \u201Cit feels illegal to feel
    this good\u2026"
